    def min_coin_count(value, coin_list):
    count = 0

    for coin in sorted(coin_list, reverse=True):
        count += (value // coin)
        value %= coin

    return count

default_coin_list = [100, 500, 10, 50]

print(min_coin_count(23520, default_coin_list))
print(min_coin_count(32590, default_coin_list))
